hcl.epitrack.ontologygenerator.object

Class XLSXMapperRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • hcl.epitrack.ontologygenerator.object.XLSXMapperRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RuleAS

    public class XLSXMapperRule
extends java.lang.Object
implements RuleAS
    XLSXMapperRule objects correspond to complex concept or individual axiom set generation rules and use metadata parameter that can be set after the object construction. They use MappingMaster API syntax to define rules in Manchester Syntax (https://github.com/protegeproject/mapping-master/wiki)
    Author:
    melissa
    See Also:
    interface
